        <akn:heading>Director.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_50-921_02_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The DDOT shall be headed by a Director. The Director shall be appointed by the Mayor with the advice and consent of the Council pursuant to ยง 1-523.01(a).</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_50-921_02_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Director shall have authority over DDOT, its functions and personnel, including the power to re-delegate to employees authority as, in the judgment of the Director, is warranted in the interests of efficiency and sound administration.</akn:p></akn:content>
